{
  "stem": "13096.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every night, after, you know, we went to bed on Shabbat, she would sing all the same songs from the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she will, you know, keep us like-- like going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, you know, it came October.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we arrive, it was August.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It came October, and it was Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That year it fell in 1944, it fells in Yom Kippur, on October-- in October.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, you know, of course we say, today's Kippur, we won't eat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, we ask-- we ask the [GERMAN] to-- you know, to intervene to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If the food-- our food of that night of Kippur, could be given to us the next-- the next day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then they say, yes, they will give it to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Come the next day, we're all, you know, fasting, it was Kippur.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The next day came, they're giving us nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because say, you didn't want to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it's Kippur.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We didn't eat that-- that night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- you know, beside that, you know, the-- when it was, you know, any other festival, we knew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't know how I knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We had no calendar.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We know when it was Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We knew everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Though we were working, but we were trying to-- to remember, how it was, the good times, when we were in Rhodes Island. how it was, the shul, how it was.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were talking each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Otherwise, we were just, you know, lucky enough to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were like beasts, I can tell you the truth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were not, you know, like-- we had no feelings for nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had no feelings for nothing, you see?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
